page.title: 20CLASS SEVEN
page.content: The Domesday project was carried out in St.Mary's school by class seven. Class seven consists of; D.Kerner, N.Townsend, C.Cornish, S.Doherty, S.Whitmore, C.Hutchinson, C.Molyneux, T.Brown, L.Cornish, A.Reeve, S.Thomas, E.Connett, K.Lundy, L.Francis, D.Fitzpatrick, I.Price, D.Stoner, M.Parsons, T.Fitzgerald, I.Griffiths, M.Parsons, N.Giles, M.Cornelius, C.Julyan, K.Salter, S.Difford, A.Lawson, N.Masters, D.Williams, S.Parker, J.Quinton, T.May, S.Luxton, Chu Ming Wong, M. Hedger. Class seven worked under the direction of Mrs.D.Pescod and Mrs.S.Hicks.
